The paper deals with Knowledge Base Question Answering, which is a subfield of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Artificial Intelligence (AI). The use of Gated Graph Neural Networks also suggests a focus on machine learning and graph-based models, which are common in subfields such as Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with data sets and error analysis, which are common in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Databases (cs.DB).
